    "48c4de850cb436ad5adcae044ea5a7be4756268a2ff172bc53f27869aaf1962f": "Thank you, [?]. However, this is quite embarrassing... but I don't think I have the strength to take them myself.",
    "f9f4afdd75e5bbfd966115b421da3928faae2ed00af5a6e9046ff0ebe287cd48": "I think so. Thanks, [?].",
    "d084aafb9896214a3d026aa88b9fecfe8c021fc3064e0aa25b6869437527b3fa": "Thank you, [?]. I see you managed to find yourself a disguise to use. For this to work, I'll need one as well.",
    "5fabb21ead9f0877d8a83c89a76181c4564c1bc732c93a08ef4e1135b4956978": "Hello again, [?]. Any luck finding that disguise?"
